@startuml 14-登录授权顺序图
' =========================================================================
' 慧医数字医疗应用系统 -- 登录与授权顺序图（Sequence Diagram）
' 阶段：动态建模
' 参与者：Vue客户端 / AuthController / AuthService / AccountMapper / TokenService / Redis / PermissionService / PermissionMapper
' =========================================================================
skinparam shadowing false
autonumber

actor "管理员/医生" as U
participant "Vue 客户端\n(request.js)" as V
participant "AuthController" as AC
participant "AuthService" as AS
participant "AccountMapper" as AM
participant "TokenService" as TS
database "Redis" as R
participant "PermissionService" as PS
participant "PermissionMapper" as PM

== 登录 ==
U -> V : 输入用户名/密码
V -> AC : POST /api/login (form-urlencoded)
AC -> AS : login(username, password)
AS -> AM : findByUsername(uname)
AM --> AS : Account{pwd, utype, status}
AS -> AS : BCrypt.matches + status==1 校验
alt 账号或密码错误/禁用
  AS --> AC : BusinessException(LOGIN_FAILED)
  AC --> V : {code:错误, message}
  V --> U : 提示错误
else 校验通过
  AS -> TS : create(AuthSession)
  TS -> R : SET prefix+sha256(token) = JSON(session) TTL 30m
  TS --> AS : token
  AS --> AC : LoginResult{token, userInfo{utype}}
  AC --> V : {code:20000, data:LoginResult}
  V -> V : localStorage.setItem("token")
end

== 加载动态菜单/路由 ==
V -> PS : GET /api/permissions (Authorization: token)
note right of V : store.dispatch("app/setMenuList")
PS -> TS : find(normalizeAuthorization(token))
TS -> R : GET prefix+sha256(token)
R --> TS : JSON(session)
TS --> PS : AuthSession{utype}
PS -> PM : 查 role_permission + permission (按 utype)
PM --> PS : 权限列表
PS -> PS : 构建菜单树 PermissionNode
PS --> V : 权限树 (管理员全量 / 医生只读子集)
V -> V : Vuex 存 menuList + router.addRoutes
V --> U : 跳转 /home，渲染侧边菜单

== 退出登录 ==
U -> V : 点击退出
V -> AC : POST /api/logout (Authorization: token)
AC -> TS : delete(token)
TS -> R : DEL prefix+sha256(token)
AC --> V : {code:20000}
V -> V : localStorage.removeItem("token")
V --> U : 跳转 /user/login

note over V, R
  <b>安全要点</b>
  - 不信任客户端 roleName，角色取自 Redis 会话
  - Redis key 用 SHA-256(token)，不存原始 Token
  - Token 失效返回 code=10006，前端自动跳登录
end note

@enduml
